{
  "stem": "1917.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I-- I did not talk to it about it to my sister, or to my aunt, or to my uncle, because my aunt married somebody who lost all his family.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I just developed-- I took the soap.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We buried it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I developed severe nightmares.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was dreaming nightly that I was washing with soap.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the soap would turn into the voices of my parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would yell at me, why do you wash with me?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would break out in a terrible sweat and began screaming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would wake up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could not wash with soap for years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't even talk to Miriam about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We still were not at the point where I could communicate with anybody any of my feelings, any of my thoughts.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Finally, the nightmares ended when we went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, there is one little story that you probably-- since you asked me about anti-Semitism-- yes, there sure was anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a rumor-- in Kolozsvar-- Cluj-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yeah, first of all, we lived with my aunt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we had very little food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We ate in an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we would go there at noon, eat something, and then we would go back to school, and we would go there at night and eat dinner there, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we would take some milk for breakfast home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well the rumor was that there was a vampire-- a Jewish vampire-- who was attacking people on the street.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Since we had to walk after school, it was quite a distance to the orphanage to get our food and our milk, because you couldn't get milk any other way.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
